spells.description:
Equip: Every 6 sec, Zap your target and 1 nearby enemy for 20,845 Nature damage.

Casting 30 spells Turbo-Charges you for 15 sec, doubling the frequency of your Zaps and upgrading them into Giga-Zaps, dealing 62,536 Nature Damage instead.

Use: Reignite the pilot light to gain 8,794 Intellect for 15 sec. After casting 3 harmful spells, it unleashes a beam dealing 1.7 million Fire damage to your primary target and 141,456 damage to up to 5 enemies in its path. (2 Min Cooldown)
Use: Zap yourself for 241,981 Nature damage, gaining 14,594 Intellect for 15 sec. (45 Sec Cooldown)
